    "description": {
      "description": "<p class=\"SubNome2\">Corpo a corpo</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Com movimentos das mãos e braços faz crescer a partir da pele e vestes vinhas fortes que se estendem com espinhos venenosos.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Esforço (ao criar):</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> retém 10.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo de preparo (ao criar):</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 1 ação.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 3m.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 9+FIS/DES/2.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> Indireto, se o ataque causar ao menos 1 de dano, alvo recebe </span>[3+COG|ESP+4<span lang=\"JA\" style=\"font-family:'MS Mincho';mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">Ⓐ</span>] de dano Biológico: Tóxico, teste de Saúde (dif18) reduz o dano pela metade.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos (ao criar):</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> pode atacar assim que criado.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Perícias:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> Briga ou Druidismo-1.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Pré-requisitos:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> <em>Cipó</em> e Druidismo N6.</span></p>",
